ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Clutch is brainwashed by the brainwave scanner and helps capture Rock & Roll so he can be subjected to the same. Darklon completes his deal with Benzheen while Airtight & Dusty meet the country's former emir in prison. Hawk assembles a strike team led by Lt. Falcon to rescue their Benzheen operatives, then assigns Jinx to a separate, secret mission.
